auty-desire.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aBody image in women. 0aFeminist theory. 0aHuman bodyxSocial aspects. 0aSelf-perception in women. 0aSurgery, Plastic. 0aWomenxPhysiology. 4aCultural Studies : Body, The. 4aCultural Studies : Cultural Studies. 4aGender and Sexuality : Women's Studies. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Gender Studies.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertSUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013z978311148737340uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780791484333423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780791484333/original  a978-3-11-148737-3  SUNY Press eBook Package  Backlist 2000-2013c2000d2013  aGBV-deGruyter-alles